metadata.name: Mojo
metadata.description:
Premium Urban Downtown:  10k per parcel
Enjoy a high density experience with these parcels. Own stunning high-rise outdoor spaces, rooftop views, with a modern-urban vibe. Just a short distance to event venues, collaborative spaces, providers, leased properties, in a rich, faster-paced social atmosphere.  Owners of these parcels enjoy premium same-day tech support, 7 days per week.
